{
  "stem": "18932.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't understand how-- I don't know what happened to the baby, whether they lived, because we were so-- we weren't concerned with anybody else.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was just-- to survive, and you know, everybody was really self-centered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many a times, my mom would give me a piece of her bread, and I really shouldn't have taken it, but I did.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Because I was so hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she was-- she would-- she would share anything with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I feel very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the time, I only-- I only pray to God I should be-- I should be freed on my birthday, and my wish was granted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were freed on April 15, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The English, the British.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came, and they started saying, hello, hello, with those loudspeakers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you have to stay here another three days, then we'll be able to get you out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a lot of people that, in those three days, got killed because they run to the gates, and the gates were still electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they would just-- you could see them stuck to the gates.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of people were shot, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Hungarians-- Hungarian military were still around, and if somebody wanted to escape they would-- shot them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was just-- a lot of people died yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember that the kapo, the Czech kapo, she liked me, and she knew it was my birthday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she gave me an extra-- there was a soup that we used to get still there, one soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she gave it to me and she says she wishes all my life I should have such lucky days as today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was-- she was nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She liked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
